OL,3,CMajor Teesside employer British Steel
OL,4,Cbrought into public ownership
OL,6,FBritish Steel, which employs hundreds
OL,7,Fof people on Teesside, has been
OL,8,Fbrought under public control.
OL,10,FThe firm operates two long product
OL,11,Fmills, in Redcar and at Skinningrove
OL,12,Fin East Cleveland.
OL,14,FThe government said the move will
OL,15,Fprotect thousands of jobs nationally,
OL,16,Fsafeguarding supply chains, major
OL,17,Finfrastructure projects and national
OL,18,Fsecurity.
OL,20,FThis is a breaking story. More details
OL,21,Fto follow...
